&gt; actions , both dastardly and saintly, seem to have some very 
&gt; real affect on your ability to play the game....this is 
&gt; GOOD...good in the sense that peopel in Norrath will be forced 
&gt; to behave within certain guidelines just like people in teh real 
&gt; world are forced to behave within certain guidelines.......now 
&gt; you'll all say &quot;...but i don't want no r00ls, that shIt is 
&gt; for FaGs....i WaNnA d0 wHAt i WanT....If I WanT to r0l3Play a 
&gt; eViLL(tm) cHar, Th3N i ShouLd b3 abL3 to&quot;.....the truth is, 
&gt; you want to play quake, and you want to force everyone to play 
&gt; quake with you.......killing anyone who happens to walk by is 
&gt; NOT roleplaying....roleplaying is behaving the way you believe 
&gt; your character would behave in some fantasy setting......in any 
&gt; reasonable society people are punished for killing 
&gt; innocents....you char would know this before he started killin 
&gt; innocents and wouldn't do it...if he did, he would be punished 
&gt; severly (prolly killed, which would make your in-game experince 
&gt; a little different, eh?).... 

&gt; so NOW, you jokers are placed into a situation where you will be 
&gt; forced to roleplay, where the world will fight back(just like 
&gt; the real world) against it's criminal element and you're all 
&gt; crying the blues about it....well cry me a river, monkey boy, 
&gt; cause that's the way it is.....maybe this PvP server is a good 
&gt; idea after all, it's actually a brilliant move on Verant's 
&gt; part...they can quarantine al you assholes and isolate you from 
&gt; people who want to actually play Everquest as opposed to 
&gt; EverQuake......for the cost of another server and whatever 
&gt; they're paying geiger, they can maintain their initial 
&gt; game-design vision without the likes of you ruining it for 
&gt; everyone else nd turn it into something it's not supposed to 
&gt; be..... 

&gt; so, in a sense, you win.....you get your &quot;serial killer 
&gt; world&quot;....have at it, jerk off.....but for god's sake if i 
&gt; see one more post on this board demanding that Verant re-write 
&gt; all their code to amke the game more fun for you guys, i'll go 
&gt; mad.........in this case, my friends, you guys are the 
&gt; minority...the game wasn't designed with you in mind and won't 
&gt; be re-written to accomodate you...you're lucky enough that you 
&gt; have your own server 

&gt; in the end, i believe PvP is doomed........Verant will NOT 
&gt; re-write huge chunks of code (basically, what you seem to be 
&gt; asking is for them to throw their whole level/skills out the 
&gt; window and re-do it just for you) to accomodate you (whom 
&gt; &quot;normal&quot; players consider to be a very annoying 
&gt; degnerate case)......you d00ds are typical regarded as a probelm 
&gt; that a game must be designed around....the bottom line is that 
&gt; Verant, in all likeliehood, will honor NONE of your requsts and 
&gt; you'll be playing the game, in respect to PvP, just as it is now 
&gt; for a good long time .......there just simply isn't enough time 
&gt; to develop two games concurrently and you'll be the ones that 
&gt; are sacrificed for the good of the other........once the light 
&gt; of day fianlly filters thru your thick skulls and you REALIZE 
&gt; that PvP was put into ths game as an afterthought and this 
&gt; REALLY isn't meant to be a PvP game, you'll get bored 
&gt; (hopefully) and go back to UO or wherever it is you came from 
